                <button type="button" class="close close-sm" data-dismiss="alert"> <i class="fa fa-times"></i> </button>
                <strong>说明：</strong>填写从2010年1月以后发生变更的情况。</div>
                        <form class="form-horizontal" role="form" action="/EnterFile/_AddIndustryChange" method="post">
						<h5 style="background:#eff2f7; font-weight:bold; color:#65cea7; line-height:30px; padding-left:20px; border-radius:4px;">配偶、子女及其配偶从业变更情况</h5>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="inputEmail1" class="col-lg-3 col-sm-2 control-label">从业变更人员</label>
